{"about_the_game":"Balocks is a casual arcade game designed for those who enjoy arranging pieces without leaving spaces. With a unique twist, you move all the pieces simultaneously! Combine pieces in a 4x4 block or larger to clear them and earn points. Enhance your combo, aim for a high score, and unlock new backgrounds and palettes as you progress!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103340/extras/shift_all.gif?t=1724356852\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Game Modes</h2>Balocks features two game modes: <br><br>In <strong>Normal Mode</strong>, challenge yourself to achieve high scores by clearing blocks and maintaining your combo within a 5-minute limit. Every move counts, can you think fast and score high when the clock is ticking?<br><br>For a more relaxed experience, try <strong>Zen Mode</strong>. You can play without worrying about scores or losing. Just enjoy merging blocks at your own pace. Zen Mode is perfect for unwinding after a long day or just to enjoy the flow of the game.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103340/extras/different_game_modes.gif?t=1724356852\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Style Customization</h2>Personalize your experience with a variety of backgrounds and color variations for the block pieces. Make the game follow your style!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103340/extras/various_styles.gif?t=1724356852\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103340/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1724356852","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103340/page.bg.jpg?t=1724356852","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103340/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1724356852","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/